text: Andrey Pyshnik (; ; born 1 February 1968) is a former Belarusian footballer and currently a coach. From summer 2016 till the end of 2017 he was the head coach of Torpedo Minsk.Pyshnik appointed as a new Torpedo Minsk head coach ==Honours== MPKC Mozyr *Belarusian Premier League champion: 1996 ==References== ==External links== * Profile at teams.by * Profile at pressball.by * Profile at Soccerway Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Minsk Category:Soviet footballers Category:Belarusian footballers Category:FC Alga Bishkek players Category:FC Akzhayik players Category:FC Vitebsk players Category:FC Torpedo Minsk players Category:FC Ataka Minsk players Category:FC Slavia Mozyr players Category:FC RUOR Minsk players Category:Belarusian football managers Category:FC Minsk managers Category:FC Torpedo Minsk managers Category:Association football midfielders
